m/hl-devos-votd\n      - link \"RSS\" [ref=e53]:\n        - /url: https://feeds.feedburner.com/hl-devos-votd\n  - heading \"Previous Devotionals\" [ref=e54] [level=3]\n  - link \"Previous Day (April, 30, 2026)\" [ref=e55]:\n    - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/en/04302026/\n  - link \"Browse by Date\" [ref=e56]:\n    - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/archives/en/\n  - link \"Next Day (May, 2, 2026)\" [ref=e57]:\n    - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/en/05022026/\n  - heading \"About\" [ref=e58] [level=3]\n  - paragraph:\n    - text: Verse of the day is currently read by over 1 million people each month. This ministry is supported by generous readers all over the world!\n    - link \"Donate to this Ministry\" [ref=e59]:\n      - /url: /support/\n  - paragraph:\n    - text: VerseoftheDay.com was started in 1998 by\n    - link \"Ben Steed\" [ref=e60]:\n      - /url: http://bensteed.com\n    - text: and became part of the\n    - link \"Heartlight\" [ref=e61]:\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org\n    - text: Network in 2000.\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Heartlight Logo\" [ref=e62]:\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org\n  - heading \"More Daily Devos:\" [ref=e63] [level=3]\n  - heading \"Praying with Paul\" [ref=e64] [level=4]:\n    - link \"Praying with Paul\" [ref=e65]:\n      - /url: http://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/praying_paul/pwp.pl\n  - text: Features the apostle Paul's writings turned into daily, powerful prayers.\n  - link \"Read Today's 'Praying with Paul' Devotional\" [ref=e66]:\n    - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/praying_paul/pwp.pl?121\n  - text: \"'All Things in Order' (1 Co. 14:26-33)\"\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"\\\" [ref=e67]Dear Father, God of intelligibility and peace, When we come together and each of us has something to contribute, may everything be done to build up.....\\\"\":\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/praying_paul/pwp.pl?121\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Subscribe to Praying with Paul\" [ref=e68]:\n      - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/subscribe.php?lang=pwp&KeepThis=true&TB_iframe=true&height=300&width=445\n      - text: Subscribe to Praying with Paul\n  - heading \"Morning & Evening\" [ref=e69] [level=4]:\n    - link \"Morning & Evening\" [ref=e70]:\n      - /url: http://www.heartlight.org/spurgeon/\n  - text: The classic twice-daily devotional from Charles H. Spurgeon.\n  - link \"Read Today's 'Morning & Evening' Devotional\" [ref=e71]:\n    - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/spurgeon/0501-am.html\n  - text: \"Morning Thought: Song of Songs 5:13\"\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"\\\" [ref=e72] [nth=1]Lo, the flowery month is come! March winds and April showers have done their work, and the earth is all bedecked with beauty. Come my soul, put on...\\\"\":\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/spurgeon/0501-am.html\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Subscribe to Morning & Evening\" [ref=e73]:\n      - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/subscribe.php?lang=me&KeepThis=true&TB_iframe=true&height=300&width=445\n      - text: Subscribe to Morning & Evening\n  - heading \"Spiritual Warfare\" [ref=e74] [level=4]:\n    - link \"Spiritual Warfare\" [ref=e75]:\n      - /url: http://www.heartlight.org/spiritualwarfare/\n  - text: A daily devotional about God's power for our battles.\n  - link \"Read Today's 'Spiritual Warfare' Devotional\" [ref=e76]:\n    - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/spiritualwarfare/en/0501/\n  - text: \"'Our Place of Encouragement' (He. 10:24-25)\"\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"\\\" [ref=e77] [nth=2]We must also consider how to encourage each other to show love and to do good things. We should not stop gathering together with other believers, as....\\\"\":\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/spiritualwarfare/en/0501/\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Subscribe to Spiritual Warfare\" [ref=e78]:\n      - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/subscribe.php?lang=sw&KeepThis=true&TB_iframe=true&height=300&width=445\n      - text: Su